{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>New Recruit!</i> It's time to get Mug-Making and keep the face factory afloat in <strong><i>FACE LOVE: Face Designer! </i></strong>Take a shift at the Face Tec factory, using strangers' Love Profiles' as inspiration to make them brand new faces.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/Customer_Banner_1.png?t=1739555683\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/divider_line.png?t=1739555683\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/replayability.png?t=1739555683\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A <strong>new selection of customers and face parts</strong> each time you play! Get creative and work with the parts you're given to complement the customer's personality.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/share_creations.png?t=1739555683\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Save <strong>high quality images</strong> of your customers in <strong>Photo Mode</strong>. Choose from a selection of backgrounds to find one that matches your customer!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/creative_mode.png?t=1739555683\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Brand new ways to customize your saved faces, with the <strong>Renamer</strong> tool, <strong>body and head recoloring</strong>, and a gallery of <strong><u>over 200+ face parts</u></strong>. Make a brand new face, or improve an existing customer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/face_library.png?t=1739555683\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">All your faces from Play Mode and Creative Modes are saved to the Library. Browse your creations, or  return and edit   them further!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><i>C'mon recruit, there's money to be made!!!</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/divider_line.png?t=1739555683\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/LLSteamBanner.png?t=1739555683\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">LimboLane is a creative duo making silly games that squish and bounce, comprised of designer Day Lane and animator Yugo Limbo. They have a love for the kitschy, the surreal, and the utterly bizarre. They're known for the nod-and-shake puzzle game <u><i><strong>Smile For Me</strong></i></u> and the a-pocky-lips stopping adventure <u><i><strong>Great God Grove</strong></i></u>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/Customer_Banner_2.png?t=1739555683\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/extras/divider_line.png?t=1739555683\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3401050?t=1739555683","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3401050?t=1739555683","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/c05bc71f480eac866d255bf5c7c158ab5e7f3cae/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739555683","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3401050/c05bc71f480eac866d255bf5c7c158ab5e7f3cae/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739555683",